author: rhuijben
msg: Implement the uri specific parts of svn_uri_is_root, svn_uri_basename
and svn_uri_dirname. Before this commit the only recognized root was "/".
(uri_previous_segment): Use uri_schema_root_length to keep the root as a
single segment. This makessvn_uri_basename and svn_uri_dirname schema-
(svn_uri_is_root): Use uri_schema_root_length to determine if the passed
uri is a schema defined root.
(svn_uri_basename): Return "" as basename when the passed uri is a root
(test_uri_is_root): Add extra tests on new behavior.
(test_uri_basename): Remove expected failure on http root and add
(test_uri_dirname): Remove expected failure on http root and add
